<div class="nav-container">
    <h4>About</h4>
    <p class="heading-nav">About MyBlog</p>
    <p>MyBlog is a simple blogging platform where users can read and share interesting articles on different topics. The goal of this website is to provide a space where ideas, knowledge, and experiences can be shared with others. Visitors can explore posts, learn new things, and stay updated with different topics.</p>

    <p class="heading-nav">Purpose of the Website</p>
    <p>This website was created as part of a learning project while studying web development. It helps demonstrate how a blogging platform works, including creating, displaying, and managing blog posts using modern web technologies.</p>

    <p class="heading-nav">Technologies used</p>
    <p>This project is built using modern web technologies such as HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, Node.js, Express.js, and MongoDB. These technologies help create a responsive and dynamic blogging platform.</p>

    <p class="heading-nav">About the Developer</p>
    <p>This website was developed by a student learning full-stack web development. The project is part of a learning journey to understand how real-world web applications are designed and built.</p>
